Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Woke up with yawning,\Nit's dawning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Turned on my radio\NTo start up new day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As goddamed D.J. chattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing news got over\NOn that air wave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:49.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:50.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:01:01.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-night, good-night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:24.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you some other day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:48.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to watch me.\NI won't go--!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:53.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:56.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Koga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:12.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice.\NKariya is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:13.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try to take me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeige dih, Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeige dih, Dalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:51.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:01.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Do you need my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a hopeless person…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay. I love to fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like chasing you\Neven more if you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful… I'm getting excited…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:55.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?\NThere're stairs over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:40.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:51.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… I'm hot…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She can still move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my…\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who will accept them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! You came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Accept…my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… You disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How rude… I know.\NYou want me to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not good to be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take my time and enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't harm the Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:07.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can do what I like to the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to\Nbe protecting me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't protect you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:42.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just decided I wouldn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:50.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer want to be a burden…\Nnor will I be made a key person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful! I'm delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice manly thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:00.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You make me want to hug you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:09.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:12.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's already disappeared,\Nbut there was a sign of two Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine,\Nbut try not to be seen by people…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!\NHow rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange for four stuffed animals\Nto be walking around…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't choose this look\Nto begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting up with this\Nbecause I can't get out of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine! Is that so…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:48.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh ho. This is definitely suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? There are traces of\NIshida's Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:53.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:54.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:10.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.\NIshida was brought here…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's fire.\NWhich means it's that woman and…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The other one…\Nis someone we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they were fighting\Nover the Quincy…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were fighting for Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This set up…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is it a “Princess Uryu Ishida Story”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:35.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! How disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… It kind of matches…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:44.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! I'm burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was hot…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba… You can suck in flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:52.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:54.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida's bandages…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can someone follow\NIshida's Spirit Ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:07.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida's Spiritual Pressure is very weak\Nand he's suppressing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:13.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He won't even let us know\Nif he's been caught by Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:21.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, we may be able\Nto follow the Bounts' reishi residue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:22.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I'm frustrated…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My powers would be better\Nif I was in a gigai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:33.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We mod-souls' real bodies are small pills…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:38.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't walk or even speak\Nunless someone puts us in a gigai…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:45.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I've always thought\Nit was strange, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then why don't you put each other\Ninto your gigai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:10.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up with that?!\NHe didn't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that! I knew,\Nbut I just acted like I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how could I have missed that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:19.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely an example\Nof people not being aware
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of their surroundings,\Nor a Copernican revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew, but I was acting dumb on purpose!\NOf course, I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nlet's go after the Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What about me?!\NI'm the only stuffed animal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:50.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tenth Squad Captain Hitsugaya,\Nand Lieutenant Rangiku Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:55.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eleventh Squad Captain Zaraki,\Nand Lieutenant Yachiru Kusajishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Entering.\N– Entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing at\Na time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you were regular squad members
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you would be my pet’s food\Nbecause you were incompetent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake, what did you\Nwant to talk to us about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:15.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who wanted to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I summoned everyone here because…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,General Captain Yamamoto\Nis not here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:29.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then. Twelfth Squad Captain\NKurotsuchi will explain the details…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are no details!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's my databank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:37.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has been breaking in\Nand looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:40.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at it? Looking at what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:44.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would it surprise you if I said…Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the enemy planted a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would destroy all the data\Nif it was removed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what this means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:06.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is both a challenge and\Na great insult towards me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:10.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the head of the Department\Nof Research and Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If someone here is involved\Nwith the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,give me your name immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:20.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pickle you in a pool of acid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop picking a fight, Kurotsuchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:28.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're high-ranking officials of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:31.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already forgotten\Nthat just recently…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:35.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we were betrayed by that\Nso-called high-ranking official?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dangerous problem\Nwhich involves all of Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't act hastily…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! How unreliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if anyone does anything else\Nto make me look foolish…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:58.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,be prepared, because I have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:10.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Kurotsuchi incident and\Nthe fact that we found Ichinose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:21.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are worried about Maki, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It just all seems fishy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mansion that fits the description\Na little further down from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:39.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:43.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be an incredibly\Nrich man who lives there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but no one has ever seen him…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya won't forgive you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I'm lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:08.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then come out of this room\Nand meet Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you can't even get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:21.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't try anything stupid like\Nusing your doll in that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge garden…\NI can't see the house…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NLet's split up and search for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:50.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to see the Quincy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Koga caught him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's in the hall right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's our valuable trump card…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll greet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I advance our plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holding back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve lived for a long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:35.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that time, all of our memories\Nhave become coated in gray…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:41.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in a while,\NI can see the world in color.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:45.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wrong if I wish to\Nenjoy this a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, however…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:48.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:52.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Udagawa, you don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:01.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts' Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Being this close I can clearly tell;\Neven without the mod-souls…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:15.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are…five, six, seven…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,eight of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:22.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since we don't know their plan,\Nwe can’t waste time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural to be cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've given you quite a rough invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jin Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:14.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to borrow your Quincy powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to gain the power\Nof Hueco Mundo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no changing the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:29.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that we are both rejected beings…\Ndue to our unique abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unique abilities…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I have a proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:38.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can we live cooperatively together,\Ninstead of acting like enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bounts can protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:48.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, we may be able to\Nrevive your lost power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think\Nthat's a good proposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know I have no powers, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. We're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's understandable to be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:11.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can wait until you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forever in fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on confining me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dalk, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:54.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… This is my prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya is a kind, but terrifying person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We headed straight towards\Nthe mansion, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I wonder which way it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to get\Na hold of my sense of direction…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! This is also the wrong way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This mansion has too many extensions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the only thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:42.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:46.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something is messing up our senses…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be mineral veins or\Nthe effects of a strong magnetic force?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've been discovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:54.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Red Flame Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows… But this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:40.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I don't want to make\Na big fuss, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:43.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh ho?! Could those things\Ncoming behind you be…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba! Erase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:02.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The house was filled with\Nthose strange eyeball dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:06.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba erased them,\Nbut they just kept creeping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was no end to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we went outside…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:12.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't expect them\Nto be outside as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they won't let us rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:23.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:43.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… That's a pretty\Nimpressive tapestry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This depicts witch hunting…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…that's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:17.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reaper Substitutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky blue dreams shine and flicker,\Ndancing away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:34.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers glow and fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:50.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sky falls silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:56.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as a pair of\Ndreamy fireworks (Hanabi) lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will sing my piercing love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:08.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:13.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blooming in an instant\Nare fireworks (Hanabi)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:21.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky blue dreams shine and flicker,\Ndancing away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:25.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blossom away in full bloom, high above
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:30.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Protect and keep those feelings thriving
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:36.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strongly, at least till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:44.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These flowers will glow and fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:57.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lirin, where did you hide your gigai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Under your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone finds it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:01.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:06.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hid it with a doll set and made it\Nlook as if it was a secret hobby of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:08.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone finds it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret hobby…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:20.65,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:22.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:28.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must endure!\NI can't show my shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.02,0:24:30.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.09,0:24:34.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! Tetsuzaemon, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.63,0:24:38.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Nothing…\NI just have a bit of a stomach-ache…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.17,0:24:39.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The toilet is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.74,0:24:41.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:46.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.33,0:24:50.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:58.64,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!